data.text:
Celebrate the holidays with Sounds of the Season, a WYSO tradition produced by NBC15. Sounds of the Season features performances by WYSO’s Youth Orchestra, Opus One, the WYSO Percussion Ensemble, the Tibbetts Brass Quintet, and local high school music groups. The program airs on NBC15 on Monday, December 24 at 10 pm and Tuesday, December 25 at 6 am.

You can view the 2017 version of Sounds of the Season here.
